OL,3,CConstruction firm collapse leaves
OL,4,Cpeople #20 million out of pocket
OL,6,FThe Guernsey contractors who are
OL,7,Ffacing a #20 million shortfall after
OL,8,Fthe collapse of construction company
OL,9,FHurel Limited, formerly RG Falla, have
OL,10,Fbeen told they may never receive what
OL,11,Fthey are owed.
OL,13,FAt a creditors' meeting, those
OL,14,Faffected were briefed that a dossier
OL,15,Fof information containing serious
OL,16,Fallegations concerning the company's
OL,17,Fconduct will be handed to the police
OL,18,Fnext week (15 June).
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
