OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1781684279
OL,3,CConstruction firm collapse leaves
OL,4,Cpeople #20 million out of pocket
OL,6,FJoint Liquidator Leonard Gerber
OL,7,Fconfirmed that a five to six-figure
OL,8,Fsum of money has already been
OL,9,Frecovered, but it is not yet enough to
OL,10,Fpay any of the debts, which are in
OL,11,Fexcess of #20 million.
OL,13,FThe company had been involved in many
OL,14,Fhigh-profile projects over the years -
OL,15,Fincluding St Sampsons High School, The
OL,16,FGarenne Stand at Footes Lane, and the
OL,17,FRoyal Court buildings.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
