OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1781684279
OL,3,CConstruction firm collapse leaves
OL,4,Cpeople #20 million out of pocket
OL,6,FLegal action has also been launched
OL,7,Fagainst some of the former directors
OL,8,Ffor wrongful trading, and the meeting
OL,9,Fwas told how a number of them are
OL,10,Falleged to have flown by private jet
OL,11,Fto San Sebastian in Spain and stayed
OL,12,Fin an exclusive hotel just a few
OL,13,Fmonths before the company went into
OL,14,Fliquidation.
OL,16,FNo information has been given as to
OL,17,Fwhether the trip had been paid for by
OL,18,Fthe firm or funded independently.
OL,26,@sD@Orp
