CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1781684279
OL,3,CConstruction firm collapse leaves
OL,4,Cpeople #20 million out of pocket
OL,6,FThere are still people who owe money
OL,7,Fto Hurel, and liquidators say they
OL,8,Fremain committed to recovering what
OL,9,Fthey describe as 'substantial sums' -
OL,10,Fwhich would then be added to the pot
OL,11,Fof money to be shared out between the
OL,12,Fcreditors.
OL,14,FSince the meeting was called, some of
OL,15,Fthose debtors and former directors
OL,16,Fhave offered mediation to try to reach
OL,17,Fa financial settlement out of court.
OL,18,FIf that fails, a trial could take
OL,19,Fplace next year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
